'''Curriculum and Instruction''' (C&I) is a field within [[education]] which seeks to research, develop, and implement [[curriculum]] changes that increase student achievement within and outside schools. The field focuses on how students learn and the best ways to educate. It is also interested in new trends in teaching and learning process. It tries to find answers to questions such as "why to teach", "what to teach", "how to teach" and "how to evaluate" in instructional process. [[Master's degrees]] and [[doctorate]]s are offered at a number of [[universities]].

